snippet: Election returns cast the movement in a new light, suggesting that Moscow’s political path has diverged from the rest of the country.
abstract: Moscow's protest movement against Vladimir V Putin protest loses steam after Putin is elected Russia's president; a fourth major rally is planned, but organizers expect a small turnout; election returns cast movement in a new light, suggesting that Moscow's political path has diverged from the rest of the country.
lead_paragraph: Election returns cast the movement in a new light, suggesting that Moscow’s political path has diverged from the rest of the country.

headline.seo: After Russia Elects Putin, a Protest Wanes
headline.main: Though One More Rally Is Set, a Protest Wanes in Post-Election Russia
